{"word":"H7378 - רִיב - rîyb - reeb - Adversary - எதிராளி","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>רִיב"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>rîyb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>reeb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Adversary / எதிராளி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வாக்குவாதம் பண்ணு, யுத்தம் பண்ணு, வழக்காடு, முறையிடு, வழக்கை விசாரி, வாதாடு, சண்டை பண்ணு, நியாயம் விசாரி, விரோதம், கடிந்து கொள், யாக்கேப்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to strive, to contend"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to strive"},{"paragraph":"a) physically"},{"paragraph":"b) with words"},{"paragraph":"2) to conduct a case or a legal suit, to sue"},{"paragraph":"3) to make complaint"},{"paragraph":"4) to quarrel"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil) to contend against"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>toss</i>, that is, <i>grapple</i>; mostly figuratively to <i>wrangle</i>, that is, <i>hold a controversy</i>; (by implication) to <i>defend: - </i>adversary, chide, complain, contend, debate, X ever, X lay wait, plead, rebuke, strive, X thoroughly."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3377 - יָרֵב - Yârêb - yaw-rabe'/3377\">H3377</a>, <a href=\"#/H3378 - יְרֻבַּעַל - Yᵉrubbaʻal - yer-oob-bah'-al/3378\">H3378</a>, <a href=\"#/H3380 - יְרֻבֶּשֶׁת - Yᵉrubbesheth - yer-oob-beh'-sheth/3380\">H3380</a>, <a href=\"#/H3401 - יָרִיב - yârîyb - yaw-rebe'/3401\">H3401</a>, <a href=\"#/H3402 - יָרִיב - Yârîyb - yaw-rebe'/3402\">H3402</a>, <a href=\"#/H3403 - יְרִיבַי - Yᵉrîybay - yer-eeb-ah'ee/3403\">H3403</a>, <a href=\"#/H4648 - מְפִיבֹשֶׁת - Mᵉphîybôsheth - mef-ee-bo'-sheth/4648\">H4648</a>, <a href=\"#/H4807 - מְרִיב בַּעַל - Mᵉrîyb Baʻal - mer-eeb' bah'-al/4807\">H4807</a>, <a href=\"#/H4808 - מְרִיבָה - mᵉrîybâh - mer-ee-baw'/4808\">H4808</a>, <a href=\"#/H4809 - מְרִיבָה - Mᵉrîybâh - mer-ee-baw'/4809\">H4809</a>, <a href=\"#/H4810 - מְרִי בַעַל - Mᵉrîy Baʻal - mer-ee' bah'-al/4810\">H4810</a>, <a href=\"#/H7378 - רִיב - rîyb - reeb/7378\">H7378</a>, <a href=\"#/H7379 - רִיב - rîyb - reeb/7379\">H7379</a>, <a href=\"#/H7380 - רִיבַי - Rîybay - ree-bah'-ee/7380\">H7380</a>"}]}